# Specification:

 Complete Apple Liquid Glass 2026 UI Redesign

## 1. Problem

The application already has a substantial Liquid Glass 2026 foundation, but several components and pages still use standard styling instead of the glass design system. Users experience inconsistent visual treatment across modals, dialogs, toasts, skeleton loaders, and some standard UI components, breaking the immersive glassmorphism experience.

## 2. Solution

Complete the Liquid Glass 2026 redesign by enhancing existing glass utilities, creating glass variants for remaining standard components (modals, dialogs, toasts, skeletons), adding parallax scroll effects, and ensuring consistent glass styling across all UI surfaces.

## 3.

 Acceptance Criteria

- **GIVEN** a user on any page, **WHEN** they view modals or dialogs, **THEN** these display with full glassmorphism (backdrop-blur, specular highlights, rim lights)


- **GIVEN** a user scrolling the dashboard, **WHEN** scrolling occurs, **THEN** subtle parallax depth effects are visible on background elements
- **GIVEN** a user viewing loading states, **WHEN** skeleton loaders appear, **THEN** they use glass shimmer effects matching the design system
- **GIVEN** a user receiving notifications, **WHEN** toasts appear, **THEN** they display with glass pill styling and smooth entrance animations
- **GIVEN** a user on mobile devices, **WHEN** viewing glass effects, **THEN** performance remains smooth with reduced blur values

## 4. Files to Modify

| File | Purpose | Action |
|------|---------|-----

---|
| `app/globals.css` | Add modal/dialog glass utilities, parallax CSS | modify |
| `components/ui/skeleton.tsx` | Glass shimmer skeleton loader | modify |
| `components/ui/toast.tsx` | Glass toast styling with animations | modify |
| `components/ui/button.tsx` | Add glass variant to standard button | modify |
| `components/ui/sheet.tsx` | Glass sheet/drawer styling | modify |
| `hooks/use-parallax.ts` | Parallax scroll hook for depth effects | create |
| `lib/design-system/animation-tokens.ts` | Centralized animation easing tokens | create |
| `components/ui/glass-modal.tsx` | Reusable glass modal component | create |
| `components/ui/glass-dialog.

tsx` | Glass-styled alert dialog | create |



## 5. Implementation Tasks

```tasks
- [ ] T001:

 Create animation tokens file with Apple easing curves | File:

 lib/design-system/animation-tokens.ts
- [ ] T002: Add glass modal/dialog CSS utilities to globals.css | File: app/globals.css
- [ ] T003: Create use-parallax hook for scroll-based depth effects | File: hooks/use-parallax.ts
- [ ] T004: Update skeleton component with glass shimmer effect | File: components/ui/skeleton.tsx
- [ ] T005: Update toast component with glass pill styling | File: components/ui/toast.tsx
- [ ] T006: Add glass variant to standard Button component | File: components/ui/button.tsx
- [ ] T007: Create GlassModal component with full glass treatment | File: components/ui/glass-modal.tsx
- [ ] T008: Create GlassDialog component for alerts/confirmations | File: components/ui/glass-dialog.tsx
- [ ] T009: Update Sheet component with glass sidebar styling | File: components/ui/sheet.tsx
```



## 6. Verification

- Run `pnpm dev` and navigate through all pages to verify consistent glass styling
- Test modal/dialog components for proper backdrop blur and specular highlights
- Verify skeleton loaders show glass shimmer animation
- Check toast notifications appear with glass pill styling
- Test on mobile viewport to confirm performance with reduced blur
- Verify dark mode maintains proper glass effects with adjusted opacity
- Run `pnpm typecheck` and `pnpm lint` to ensure no errors
